#A new TV streaming service was recently started in Chefland called the Chef-TV. A group of N friends in Chefland want to buy Chef-TV subscriptions. We know that 6 people can share one Chef-TV subscription. Also, the cost of one Chef-TV subscription is 
X rupees. Determine the minimum total cost that the group of N friends will incur so that everyone in the group is able to use Chef-TV.






t=int(input())
for i in range(t):
    n,x=map(int,input().split())
    if(n<6):
        print(x)
    elif(n%6==0):
        print((n//6)*x)
    else:
        print(((n//6)+1)*x)
